\c 27 27 Zvino shoko raJehovha rakasvi- kazve kwandiri, richiti, 2 "Zvino iwe, Mwanakomana womunhu, ita mariro pamusoro peTire; 3 uti kuTire, `Nhai iwe ugere pavanopinda pagungwa, iwe unoshambadzirana namarudzi avanhu pazvivi zvizhinji, zvanzi naIshe Jehovha,' iwe Tire, wakati, `Ndakakwana pakunaka.' 4 Nyika yako iri mumwoyo wamakungwa; vavaki vako vakakwanisa kunaka kwako. 5 Vakaita rnapuranga ako ose nemisipiresi inobva Seniri; vakatora musidhari weRebhanoni kukuitira danda rechikepe. 6 Matanda ako okukwasva nawo vakaaita nemiouki yeBhashani; vakaita zvigaro zvako pazvikepe nenyanga dzenzou dzakavezerwa mumapuranga emipaini yakabva kuz\hvi zvel(it√Ørrii. 7 Maseiri ako aiva omucheka wakaisvonaka, wakasonerwa hukomba, aibva Ijipiti, kuti uve mureza wako; denga rako raiva romucheka mutema nomutsvuku waibva kuzvivi zveErisha.
